		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Two things might help:<br /><ul><li>Does CV3 normally put anything in $6000-$7FFF? If not, something that'd normally be in one of the switchable banks could be relocated to PRG RAM there. </li><li>Does CV3 use the DMC? If so, the music can be rewritten not to use it, freeing up $C000-$DFFF. </li></ul>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
